Box. You&#39;ll want to purchase your chip from a reputable source or you may end up with an incompatible or faulty chip.","Also, when you install a Mod Chip into your XBox console, two things happen-first, you&#39;ll void your warranty, and second, you probably won&#39;t be able to play XBox Live-an online gamming service (with a paid subscription) which connects XBox players all over the world for gaming as if on the same system.","Whether the thought of losing your ability to eradicate aliens, clash light sabers with Jedi or battle it out on D-Day is more than you can take or if you simply want to have your XBox cake and eat it too, then backup game copies and a modified system console is the answer.","At TopTenREVIEWS We Do the Research So You Don&#39;t Have To. ","Other articles of interest:<br/><a href=\"/\">Is Game Copying Legal?</a>  <a href=\"/\">Understanding DVD Formats</a>","<a href=\"/\"><br/></a>"," "]},"id":"0ad23b3c-0cf7-4bdb-b6cb-cc96871c445e","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_150","url":"/copying-xbox-games-the-basics","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"jeff-ropelato","url":"/author/jeff-ropelato","dateCreated":"2019-04-18T08:03:59Z","name":"Jeff Ropelato","dateModified":"2019-04-18T08:03:59Z","id":"ZFTp4R9MHcSeWJm9weTSoE","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","datePublished":"2010-10-18T18:56:52Z","name":"Copying XBox Games: The Basics","synopsis":"With hundreds of dollars invested into Xbox gaming systems, many people are looking for ways to better protect their investment-making backup game copies has become a popular alternative.","review":{},"strapline":"With hundreds of dollars invested into Xbox gaming systems, many people are looking for ways to better protect their investment-making backup game copies has become a popular alternative.","language":"en","dateModified":"2010-10-18T18:56:52Z","id":"sffpARa6VNfJnpbpvWmJxN","meta":{"title":"Copyi